long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Deep Fake Detector Chrome Extension This is a Chrome extension that uses the Sightengine API to detect deep fake videos and audio on the active tab, and displays a warning popup if any deep fake content is found.
